title: BRIEF-BIMobject moves to Skanska's new building studio in Malmö
text:
BRIEF-BIMobject moves to Skanska's new building studio in Malmö 
Oct 8 BIMobject AB : 
* BIMobject has signed Skanska's lease to move to STUDIO in Malmö after it is completed 
* BIMobject will therefore relocate its headquarters in the autumn of 2016 Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage: (Gdynia Newsroom) Trending On Reuters
